                        </div>
                        <p id="fs-idp204527824">
                          An
                          <span
                            data-type="term"
                            group-by="a"
                            id="[redacted for uniqueness]"
                          >amorphous</span> substance is a material that appears to be a solid, but does not have a long-range order like a true solid. Treatment with hydrochloric acid removes the magnesium oxide. Further purification of the boron begins with conversion of the impure boron into boron trichloride. The next step is to heat a mixture of boron trichloride and hydrogen:
                        </p>
