                          <p id="fs-idp124888224">
                            All the tetrahalides of silicon, SiX
                            <sub>4</sub>, have been prepared. Silicon tetrachloride can be prepared by direct chlorination at elevated temperatures or by heating silicon dioxide with chlorine and carbon:
